Awkwr-rihq prmwqmw ny (Awpxy Awp qoN pihlW) ieh id`sdw jgq pYdw kIqw,
mwieAw dw moh BI aus ny Awpxy hukm ivc hI bxw id`qw[
ijhVw mnu`K sdw kwiem rihx vwly prmwqmw dw nwm (gurU pwsoN) sux ky (Awpxy) mn ivc vsWdw hY (aus nUM ieh inScw ho jWdw hY ik) krqwr Awp hI ieh swry Kyl kr irhw hY ]1]
(hir-nwm nUM Awpxy mn ivc vswx vwlw mnu`K ieh inScw r`Kdw hY ik) (jgq dI) mW mwieAw qoN (jgq dy ipqw prmwqmw ny swry) qRYguxI jIv pYdw kIqy (bRhmw iSv Awidk BI ausy ny pYdw kIqy),
bRhmw nUM aus ny cwry vyd (rcx leI) hukm kIqw[
vrHy mhIny vwr iQ`qW (Awidk) bxw ky ies jgq ivc (smy Awidk dI) sUJ BI auh prmwqmw hI pYdw krn vwlw hY ]2]
(prmwqmw dI imhr nwl ijs nUM gurU iml ipAw) gurU dI srn pYx qoN aus nUM ieh sRySt krn-jog kMm iml igAw,
ik prmwqmw dw nwm Awpxy ihrdy ivc vsweI r`Ko[
so, ies jgq ivc (ijs mnu`K dy ihrdy ivc) gurU dI bwxI Aw v`sdI hY, auh ies bwxI dI brkq nwl prmwqmw dw nwm pRwpq kr lYNdw hY ]3]
(pr, ijhVw mnu`K gurU dI srn qoN vWijAW rih ky vyd (Awidk hI) pVHdw hY, qy, hr vyly crcw Awidk hI krdw hY,
prmwqmw dw nwm ismrdw nhIN auh Awqmk mOq dy bMDnW ivc b`Jw rihMdw hY[
hor hor ipAwr ivc Ps ky auh sdw du`K pWdw hY[ mwieAw dy iqMn guxW dI Btkxw ivc pY ky auh jIvn dy Zlq rsqy qy ipAw rihMdw hY ]4]
gurU dy snmuK rihx vwlw mnu`K isr& prmwqmw nwl ipAwr pWdw hY,
(ies qrHW auh) mwieAw dy iqMn guxW dy kwrn pYdw hox vwly Purny nUM Awpxy mn dy ivc hI mukw dyNdw hY[
sdw-iQr pRBU dI is&q-swlwh dy Sbd dI brkq nwl auh mnu`K (ivkwrW qoN) sdw bicAw rihMdw hY, (auh Awpxy AMdroN) mwieAw dw moh dUr kr lYNdw hY ]5]
pr, ies mnu`Kw jnm ivc auh mnu`K hI nwm-rMg ivc rMgy rihMdy hn ijhVy (pihlI kIqI kmweI Anuswr) Dur drgwh qoN rMgy hoey huMdy hn[
auh gurU dI ikrpw nwl Awqmk Afolqw ivc msq rihMdy hn[
gurU dI srn pY ky mnu`K sdw pRBU dw imlwp pRwpq krI r`Kdw hY, auh Awpxy Awp nUM (pRBU dy) Awpy ivc imlw lYNdw hY ]6]
mwieAw dy moh ivc, Btkxw ivc PisAw hoieAw mnu`K prmwqmw nUM nhIN iml skdw[
hor hor ipAwr ivc l`gw hoieAw mnu`K du`K (hI) shwrdw hY[
(ksuMBy dy rMg vWg mwieAw dw) So^ rMg QoVy idn hI rihMdw hY, ies dy nws huMidAW icr nhIN l`gdw ]7]
ijhVw mnu`K (Awpxy) ies mn nUM prmwqmw dy fr-Adb ivc ipAwr ivc rMgdw hY,
auh ies rMg ivc (rMgIj ky) sdw-iQr prmwqmw ivc lIn rihMdw hY[
pr koeI ivrlw mnu`K v`fI iksmq nwl ieh pRym-rMg hwsl krdw hY[ auh gurU dI m`q au~qy qur ky ieh rMg (Awpxy mn nUM) cwVHdw hY ]8]
Awpxy mn dy ip`Cy qurn vwlw mnu`K bVw AhMkwr krdw hY,
pr auh prmwqmw dI hzUrI ivc kdy BI Awdr nhIN pWdw[
hor hor (moh) ivc l`g ky auh Awpxw mnu`Kw jnm gMvw lYNdw hY, shI jIvn dI sUJ qoN ibnw auh sdw du`K pWdw hY ]9]
myry pRBU ny Awpxy Awp nUM (hryk jIv dy) AMdr gupq r`iKAw hoieAw hY,
(iPr BI) gurU dI ikrpw nwl hI imlwieAw imldw hY[
(ijhVw mnu`K gurU dI srn pYNdw hY auh ieh smJ lYNdw hY ik) prmwqmw sdw kwiem rihx vwlw hY, aus dw nwm jpxw hI shI vxj-vpwr hY[ (gurU dI ikrpw nwl auh) kImqI hir-nwm pRwpq kr lYNdw hY ]10]
(AwpxI Akl dy Awsry) iksy mnu`K ny ies (mnu`Kw) srIr dI kdr nhIN smJI[
myry mwlk-pRBU ny iehI mrXwdw bxw r`KI hY,
ik ijhVw mnu`K gurU dy snmuK huMdw hY auh (Awpxy) srIr nUM ivkwrW qoN bcweI r`Kdw hY, Aqy Awpw-Bwv nUM Awpxy ivc hI lIn kr dyNdw hY ]11]
(hir-nwm qoN KuMiJAW) srIr dy AMdr (Awqmk jIvn dw) Gwtw pYNdw jWdw hY (nwm ivc juiVAW) srIr AMdr (Awqmk jIvn dw) lwB pRwpq huMdw hY[
gurU dy snmuK rihx vwlw mnu`K vyprvwh pRBU nUM (Awpxy srIr ivc) Bwldw hY[
nwm-vxj kr ky auh sdw suK mwxdw hY, Aqy hr vyly Awpxy Awp nUM Awqmk Afolqw ivc itkweI r`Kdw hY ]12]
prmwqmw dw itkwxw sdw kwiem rihx vwlw hY, aus dy ^zwny (BI) sdw kwiem rihx vwly hn[
sB kuJ dyx dI smrQw vwlw prmwqmw Awp hI (jIvW nUM ieh ^zwny) dyNdw hY[
gurU dy snmuK rihx vwlw mnu`K swry suK dyx vwly prmwqmw dI is&q-swlwh krdw hY, aus nUM Awpxy mn ivc sWB r`Kdw hY, aus (dy nwm) dI kdr smJdw hY ]13]
mnu`K dy srIr dy ivc hI nwm-pdwrQ hY, pr mnu`K ies dI kdr nhIN smJdw[
